            "title": "Practical Example: Counter 🔢",
            "content": "# Real-World Usage\n\nAssignment operators are perfect for:\n\n* **Counters:** `count += 1`\n* **Accumulators:** `total += price`\n* **Score tracking:** `score -= penalty`\n* **Progress bars:** `progress += 10`"
        },
