            "title": "Counter Pattern 💻",
            "content": "A common pattern using +=:",
            "codeSnippet": "# Counting with +=\ncount = 0\n\ncount += 1  # First item\ncount += 1  # Second item\ncount += 1  # Third item\nprint(\"Count:\", count)\n\n# Running total\ntotal = 0\nprices = [10, 25, 15, 30]\n\nfor price in prices:\n    total += price\n    print(f\"Added {price}, total: {total}\")",
