            "content": "## Initialize First!\n\nYou can't use += on undefined variables:\n\n```python\n# ❌ Error! count doesn't exist yet\ncount += 1\n\n# ✅ Correct\ncount = 0\ncount += 1\n```\n\nAlways initialize variables before using assignment operators!"
